      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PINGELLY PRINCE (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.24) in a Grade 6 at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings seven times from 12 attempts. Worth another chance. LARRGADI (2) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten 3 lengths (23.02) at this track in a Grade 6 over 400m. Winning chance. PINT OF SPECIAL (8) was in the minors two back (23.24) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. CHIEF WIGGUM (3) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
